      "dialogAsk": "You made it! Told you — Bunk Room's mine, I called dibs on all four corners. See that GLOW MUSHROOM sealed under the ice? It's been mocking me for a MONTH. I'd mine it myself but my pickaxe is... look, I don't HAVE my pickaxe anymore, okay? Nobody here remembers their stuff right. Crack it out, bring it here, and I'll teach you the sneakiest thing I know.",
